  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your fiend and battle endless hordes of enemies in this <strong>action-roguelike survivor</strong> game. Explore ever-changing stages, unlock new powerups and abilities, and grow stronger with every level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock more playable characters in <strong>The Fiendonomicon</strong>! Each fiend offers a unique playstyle with a <strong>passive ability </strong>and a set of <strong>4 active skills</strong>. Whether you prefer an aggressive, defensive, passive, or active approach, mastering your fiend's strengths is key to progressing through the stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage is randomly generated, offering new challenges every time. You'll find treasure chests, traps, powerful rewards guarded by enemies, and mysterious devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level up lets you choose 1 powerup from 3 options. Powerups come in two forms:<strong> Augmentations</strong>, which provide passive boosts, and <strong>Mutations</strong>, automatic weapons that trigger independently. Mix your fiend's abilities with different powerups to try new builds and wreak havoc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 playable characters, over 20 unique weapons, and much more: collect in-game currency to unlock additional content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique stages, each featuring its own enemies and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack: every stage comes with its own exclusive music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless build possibilities: combine fiend abilities with power-ups to experiment with various builds and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available on Windows, Linux and SteamOS (Steam Deck).</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/36c8ca643454cfea90adb7ad493eac29.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your fiend and battle endless hordes of enemies in this <strong>action-roguelike survivor</strong> game. Explore ever-changing stages, unlock new powerups and abilities, and grow stronger with every level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/cdc656877319637a9c6abeeded712163.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock more playable characters in <strong>The Fiendonomicon</strong>! Each fiend offers a unique playstyle with a <strong>passive ability </strong>and a set of <strong>4 active skills</strong>. Whether you prefer an aggressive, defensive, passive, or active approach, mastering your fiend's strengths is key to progressing through the stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/eab66a33048261f8c393d20ffef4f647.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage is randomly generated, offering new challenges every time. You'll find treasure chests, traps, powerful rewards guarded by enemies, and mysterious devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.poster.avif?t=1748940693\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.webm?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277650/extras/c0d06a293ab40b84667ed55edc17747a.mp4?t=1748940693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level up lets you choose 1 powerup from 3 options. Powerups come in two forms:<strong> Augmentations</strong>, which provide passive boosts, and <strong>Mutations</strong>, automatic weapons that trigger independently. Mix your fiend's abilities with different powerups to try new builds and wreak havoc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 playable characters, over 20 unique weapons, and much more: collect in-game currency to unlock additional content.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 unique stages, each featuring its own enemies and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack: every stage comes with its own exclusive music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless build possibilities: combine fiend abilities with power-ups to experiment with various builds and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available on Windows, Linux and SteamOS (Steam Deck).</p></li></ul>",
